divs: Sighting DetailsMy girlfriend and I were out taking motion photos over the QEW on the traffic. Well we didnt notice anything at the time but when we got home we were going over all the photos that we had taken tonight and noticed that triangle in the photo. This shot was done with a cannon photograghy camera and was set up for a 8 second photo. This would make moving objects blury. Those 3 lights that form the shape of a triangle showed up in 4 other photos. Not to sure if it is what it looks like so I thought I would share and googled where to send this photo so here it is.
Summary: notice strange object in 4 8second motion pics
